{"tid":865572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"怪女坐15樓窗邊 消防員「天降金剛腿」一腳踢進屋","createTime":"2018-10-17T07:28:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-17T07:59:25.000Z","uid":150685,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"25ef89eddb6d41f6ec7df381feaa14f359bde169","tid":865572,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T07:28:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3627/3627554.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3627%2F3627554.gif&h=b2669ab9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n浙江杭州有名粉衣女坐在15樓的窗戶邊，一邊前後晃腿，一邊又哭又笑。消防員接到通報後，到現場進行分工救援。在僵持一個多小時後，一名消防隊員從16樓窗戶翻進15樓，直接一腳把粉衣女踢進屋裡。<br />\n<br />\n天色暗下後，消防隊員從粉衣女樓上的窗戶翻出來，再快速踹進15樓窗戶裡，並同時將她「踢回房內」，順利完成救援，正在拍攝的鄰居也喊，「成功了成功了」，粉衣女則在無預警的情況下大聲驚呼。<br />\n<br />\n對此，網友們表示，「想活的人活不了，活著的還尋死」、「別讓消防員為自己的一時衝動搭上性命」、「踹得好」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181017/1283154.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20181017%2F1283154.htm&d=1Xpqqb4N39bP%2FPKbGsMeAk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=79af5e00\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181017/1283154.htm</a>"},{"pid":"4ba7223a379e6079d005706de3a907597c1ede7a","tid":865572,"uid":68375,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T07:32:01.000Z","msg":"該名女子被消防員踢入屋內時因頸部著地重傷，送院後不治。"},{"pid":"b757ba523be8b322f80f2b7fb3cd1a072f05810f","tid":865572,"uid":72424,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"25ef89eddb6d41f6ec7df381feaa14f359bde169","tid":865572,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T07:28:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3627/3627554.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3627%2F3627554.gif&h=b2669ab9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n浙江杭州有名粉衣女坐在15樓的窗戶邊，一邊前後晃腿，一邊又哭又笑。消防員接到通報後，到現場進行分工救援。在僵持一個多小時後，一名消防隊員從16樓窗戶翻進15樓，直接一腳把粉衣女踢進屋裡。<br />\n<br />\n天色暗下後，消防隊員從粉衣女樓上的窗戶翻出來，再快速踹進15樓窗戶裡，並同時將她「踢回房內」，順利完成救援，正在拍攝的鄰居也喊，「成功了成功了」，粉衣女則在無預警的情況下大聲驚呼。<br />\n<br />\n對此，網友們表示，「想活的人活不了，活著的還尋死」、「別讓消防員為自己的一時衝動搭上性命」、「踹得好」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181017/1283154.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20181017%2F1283154.htm&d=1Xpqqb4N39bP%2FPKbGsMeAk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=79af5e00\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181017/1283154.htm</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T07:32:49.000Z","msg":"幅圖黑到好似毒魔咁 睇條毛"},{"pid":"0ac122780741bbd2902701cee971341c68657864","tid":865572,"uid":170044,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T07:34:50.000Z","msg":"屌你老母大陸佬d手機仲係停留係144p年代"},{"pid":"bdb6ee5c276f7fe74e89010bdefd2fa51a990cf2","tid":865572,"uid":2126,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T07:35:28.000Z","msg":"踢得好, 香港應該學下咁樣對付D支那生番"},{"pid":"82eb4a47e5c5a16ffb4b0896cba8eb89fa9ea46e","tid":865572,"uid":187076,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T07:37:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cBQNGfu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcBQNGfu.jpg&h=ec9c6543&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d2c9906b88e909aa85fd42b5cf4b3d5427d798e","tid":865572,"uid":85461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T07:40:26.000Z","msg":"<strong>鐵頭功呀嗱</strong>"},{"pid":"05cee041a20e4816153c9ddc32be064c78f4c137","tid":865572,"uid":58971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T07:59:25.000Z","msg":"rainbow six?"}]}